              "step_by_step": [
                {
                  "step": "Find LCD",
                  "explanation": "Denominators are $(x+3)$ and $(x-2)$",
                  "calculation": "LCD $= (x+3)(x-2)$"
                },
                {
                  "step": "Rewrite each fraction",
                  "explanation": "Multiply to get LCD",
                  "calculation": "$\\frac{x}{x+3} \\cdot \\frac{x-2}{x-2} = \\frac{x(x-2)}{(x+3)(x-2)}$\n$\\frac{2}{x-2} \\cdot \\frac{x+3}{x+3} = \\frac{2(x+3)}{(x+3)(x-2)}$"
